data.description: This historic home, originally a 1910 Inn/Tavern, has been lovingly transformed into a magnificent 21st century home. Many of the early 20th century icons are present, highlighted by the authentic beamed ceilings, grandiose stone fireplace, and wide plank floorboards.  The over sized chefs kitchen and dinning area are fantastic for entertaining and celebrating with family and friends. On the upper level, you''ll see the current living room/media room which was once the bar & ballroom. Conveniently situated near the Taconic State Parkway, this is a commuter''s dream.  This would also be a great weekend home as well; just minutes to the many farmer''s markets and wineries in Hyde Park, Millbrook, and surrounding area.  Home inventory is limited, so this one won''t last long.  Schedule your showing appointment today.
